[src:managed-kubernetes/kubernetes] A key component of the Kubernetes control plane is the API Server, which exposes an HTTP API that can be invoked by other parts of the cluster as well as end users and external components.
[src:managed-kubernetes/kubernetes] This API is a REST API and is declarative in nature, and is the same API exposed to the control plane.
