[src:managed-kubernetes/kubernetes] In older versions of Kubernetes, the API server supported listening on both HTTP and HTTPS ports (with the HTTP port number having no transport security whatsoever).
[src:managed-kubernetes/kubernetes] This was deprecated in v1.10 and eventually dropped support in v1.20 of Kubernetes.
